tweet: @DWilps @TheStalwart Not saying you would always pick DeFi. But COULD you? Structurally seems like you can create any contract in DeFi (tools may not be there today) so equivalency is there. But the real value is in the things that can‚Äôt be done efficiently/well in TradFi.

name: Rishi Khanna
tweet: @TheStalwart Maybe think about it differently? Can you do everything you can do in TradFi in DeFi? Can you do everything you can do in DeFi in TradFi? Why would you pick one over the other given a choice.
